{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"facb079da2","title":"毛泽东关于来中央参加土改会议等问题给邓子恢的电报","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"49e38832bc","index":0,"year":1950,"month":5,"day":12,"articleId":"facb079da2"}],"tags":[{"id":"d5cbd05390","name":"通讯","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-shzygz","name":"中国五十年代初中期的政治运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-shzygz":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"2ad1eeb148","type":"title","text":"毛泽东关于来中央参加土改会议等问题给邓子恢的电报","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"facb079da2"},{"id":"8d1209a69d","type":"authors","text":"毛泽东","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"facb079da2"},{"id":"2ea35f5d64","type":"appellation","text":"子恢同志：","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"facb079da2"},{"id":"2c8fb07804","type":"paragraph","text":"（一）土改法令起草情况如何，五月十五日是否可以送达中央。（二）请令湘鄂赣三省省委各派一个熟悉情况懂得政策的同志来中央参加土改会议，如省委书记不能来则派副书记或秘书长来，中南局亦需派一个适当的同志来。以上共四人，务于五月廿三日到达中央。（三）子恢同志自己准备于六月五日左右来中央参加政协全国委员会会议，并参加中央最后决定土改法令草案之会议，何日动身，届时另电通知。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"facb079da2"},{"id":"a469c2721c","type":"paragraph","text":" 毛泽东五月十二日","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"facb079da2"}],"page":{"id":"a0ab9c8921","publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"facb079da2","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}